# chord two-voice mode: only output1/output2 connected. "Just the first two
# select inputs are taken into account." C major default -> the first two
# interval-order notes = root/3rd = C,E. pitch=0, spread=0.
#   O1=C(0), O2=E(4)
patch <<<
[chord]
    output1 = O1
    output2 = O2
>>>
@0 expect O1 0 tol 1e-5
@0 expect O2 0.0333333 tol 1e-5
